    <title>Single-Slit Diffraction</title>
  
    <video youtube="Mun7c6RB140"><description>Video description.</description></video>

    <principle>
        <title>Dark Spot Locations</title>
        <statement>
          <p>Dark spots can be determined by <m>a \mathrm{sin}\theta = p \lambda</m> for <m>p = 1, 2, 3, ...</m>.</p>
        </statement>
    </principle>

